{"title":"飞车射击","authors":["唐兆迪"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":12,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞车射击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"济南机车厂　唐兆迪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声灌满了靶场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场上飞出一只快箭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快箭牵着掌声飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啤，叱咤风雷卷云天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦眼望，呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那个“质量标兵”姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自行车上显身手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端枪、蹬车飞向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串尘浪滚滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象条金龙跟后面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一团杀气腾腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威风凛凛多不凡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见她钢枪一举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砰砰枪声震山岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛鬼蛇神应声倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靶子打得稀巴烂……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥她枪法这么准？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——汗水洗亮了枪杆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥她枪法这么狠？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——仇恨凝上了子弹！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}